Ham-Resources-Propagation version 0.01
======================================

This is the README file for Ham::Resources::Propagation, get Solar and propagation data 
from the web that's useful for Amateur Radio applications, by Carlos Juan Diaz 
<ea3hmb at gmail.com>.

After installation, please consult the tutorial for how to use it. 
'perldoc Ham::Resources::Propagation' should work on most systems.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	It requires Perl version 5.10.0 or newer

	XML::Reader
	LWP::UserAgent
	
TESTING

On 't' directory you can find a little testing script that you use after installation
for check or use directly its functions.
	
	Ham-Resources-Propagation-test.pl


